How did you and Kerry meet?
Various item, if you are looking to cause pain.
It was forty-three... or fourty-four, I can't remember. Kerry come to Memphis for a gig. At the time I was head of club security.
And, well, I make big fuck-up. Some psycho get backstage, put a knife to Kerry's throat. But he talk him out of it, pour him a tequila... When I finally get there, the crazy man was already out cold.
If Kerry tell me boss what happen... It would be bad news for me. But he feeling generous that day, keep his lips sealed. Kerry's a good man. A rare thing to find today.
